name: MediaTrackSupportedConstraints
description: The MediaTrackSupportedConstraints dictionary establishes the list of constrainable properties recognized by the user agent or browser in its implementation of the MediaStreamTrack object. An object conforming to MediaTrackSupportedConstraints is returned by MediaDevices.getSupportedConstraints().

members.name: autoGainControl
members.description: A Boolean whose value is true if the autoGainControl constraint is supported in the current environment.
